<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/an-instrument-notebook/assets/images/favicon.png">

  <title>Prelude</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --coral: #FF6F61;
      --lavender: #B3AEDF;
    }

    /* Disable overscroll bounce + ensure full viewport coverage */
    html, body {
      overscroll-behavior: none;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255,111,97,0.25), transparent 65%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(122,95,255,0.25), transparent 65%),
        linear-gradient(160deg, #05070D, #0A0F1F, #1C2541);
      color: var(--lavender);
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: block;
    }

   
    .page {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

  
    .note-cluster {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: var(--lavender);
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(199,196,226,0.7);
    }

   
    .title {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--coral);
      text-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255,111,97,0.85);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .title::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 150%;
      height: 150%;
      background: radial-gradient(
        circle,
        rgba(255,111,97,0.18),
        rgba(255,111,97,0.05) 60%,
        transparent 80%
      );
      filter: blur(18px);
      z-index: -1;
    }

    /* Content wrapper */
    .content-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .content {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--lavender);
      text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(199,196,226,0.25);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    /* Signature */
    .signature {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: right;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .signature span {
      display: inline-block;
      color: rgb(154, 154, 203);
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;
      text-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(199,196,226,0.25);
      transition: color 0.25s ease, text-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
    }

    .signature span:hover {
      color: var(--coral);
      text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .signature span:active {
      color: var(--coral);
      text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .license {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 25px;
    }

    /* Mobile glow */
    @media (hover: none) and (pointer: coarse) {
      .signature span {
        text-shadow:
          0 0 8px rgba(199,196,226,0.55),
          0 0 14px rgba(199,196,226,0.35),
          0 0 20px rgba(199,196,226,0.25);
      }
    }

    
    .home-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--coral);
      padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: rgba(255,111,97,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,111,97,0.45);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,111,97,0.55);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      transition: background 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    .home-link:hover {
      background: rgba(255,111,97,0.25);
      box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .home-link:active {
      background: rgba(255,111,97,0.25);
      box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="page">

    <div class="note-cluster">
      <div class="note">♫</div>
      <div class="note">♪</div>
      <div class="note">♫</div>
    </div>

    <div class="title">Prelude</div>

    <div class="content-wrapper">

      <div class="content">
      
       <p>
        An Instrument Notebook gathers musical instruments from different times and places, each accompanied by imagery, 
        sound, and notes. Every instrument represented here is enriched by the culture surrounding it, 
        the people who play it, and the music it lives within.
       </p>
      
      </div>

      <a class="signature" href="https://github.com/musman-uk" target="_blank">
        <span>Mohammed Usman</span>
      </a>

      <a class="home-link" href="../">An Instrument Notebook</a>

      <div class="license">© Mohammed Usman<br>
    <br> All rights reserved. No commercial use, redistribution, or derivatives.
  </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
